long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Jago is a fun adventure game where we try to move forward and get points by overcoming obstacles with an African totem.
There is an African totem in the game. We can control this totem. With the totem we can control, we try to overcome difficult obstacles. We move carefully over the obstacles and get points. We continue the game by maintaining our high score goal with the points we have achieved. Jago has emerged as an adventure game designed. With us in mind for those who love games of skill and challenge us.

To swipe Install this extension to play the Jago Game or offline with no additional downloads and no ads. 

You can contact us at support@724fun.com and share your thoughts and problems

After clicking the add the game to chrome button, you can find the game in the extensions section. If you wish, you can visit 724fun.com. If you wish, you can play again and if you want to remove it, you can remove it from the extensions section.
